<p>這邊 debig echochio-tw.github.io … 您可換您所需</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git clone https://github.com/echochio-tw/echochio-tw.github.io.git
cd echochio-tw.github.io
apt -y install ruby ruby-dev
gem install bundler
gem install jekyll
bundle install
bundle exec jekyll serve
</code></pre></div></div>

